OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJournalist fined for       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finsulting Italian PM       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A prominent Italian journalist has been
OL,6, found guilty of libel after insulting  
OL,7, Prime Minister Giorgia Meloni in a     
OL,8, television interview.                  
OL,10,FRoberto Saviano used a swear word to   
OL,11,Fdescribe Ms Meloni while attacking her 
OL,12,Fstance on migration in December 2020.  
OL,14,FHe has been handed a suspended fine of 
OL,15,F1,000 euros (#864).                    
OL,17,FThough he will only have to pay it if  
OL,18,Fhe repeats the offence,campaignerssaid 
OL,19,Fthe verdict sent a "chilling message"  
OL,20,Fabout press freedom.                   
